# Only ship what the hosted server needs. Keep the Docker build fast and the
# image small. Anything not in this include list is excluded by default.
*

# Re-include only the paths the Dockerfile COPY lines reference.
!pyproject.toml
!README.md
!src/
!hosting/

# And within those, still exclude caches, tests, and local junk.
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.pytest_cache
**/.venv
**/.env
**/.env.*
src/**/tests/
